data.meta_description: Jamuna - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Jamuna is a veteran Indian actress who has appeared in over 198 films in Telugu and other South Indian languages. She began her career in 1952 and received breakthrough success with the 1955 film Missamma. Some of her notable films include Missamma, Milan for which she won a Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress, and Pandanti Kapuram for which she received a Special Award at the Filmfares. She also ventured into politics and was elected to the Lok Sabha in 1989 before retiring.
